  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user I want to where I am when performing sign in \r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: When a user is signing in spinner disappears earlier than sign in is performed so user sees a screen with password input\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nSpinner with info message is shown all the time while sign in is being performed \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nAfter Sign in button is tapped spinner is shown for a moment and after it disappears but user is not signed in yet\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Create an account\r\n- Go to profile and log out\r\n- Select the same user, provide password and click Sign in button\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.10-782-d4145a31a+\r\n* Operating System:  LG V20, Android 7.0.0\r\n",
